In response to business growth, some companies add new IT hardware without having a
clear IT strategy or plan to keep up with that growth. What is this IT trend called?
A. cloud computing
B. consolidation
C. sprawl
D. business protection
Answer: C
What are small and midmarket companies less likely to have on their websites than
enterprise companies?
A. an annual report for the shareholders
B. details about the company's products and services
C. company news
D. a distinctive brand
Answer: A

A. Understanding the Customer Environment

Answer: D
